<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.7">
<l>kāyuṭai nelloṭu karumpamaittuk kaṭṭi yarici yavalamaittu</l>
<l>vāyuṭai maṟaiyavar mantirattāl maṉmata ṉēyuṉṉai vaṇaṅkukiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>tēyamuṉ ṉaḷantavaṉ tirivikkiramaṉ tirukkaika ḷāleṉṉait tīṇṭumvaṇṇam</l>
<l>cāyuṭai vayiṟumeṉ ṟaṭamulaiyun taraṇiyil talaippukaḻ tarakkiṟṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Preparing immature paddy and getting ready jaggery, rice, [and] pressed rice,</l>
<l>I am worshipping you, O Manmatha, with the mantras of the people of the</l>
<l rend="indent">Vedas of [good] utterance.</l>
<l>Will you be able to give [my] lustrous belly and big soft breasts the highest fame</l>
<l rend="indent">on this earth</l>
<l>In such a way that He who previously measured the land, Trivikrama, touches me</l>
<l rend="indent">with [His] sacred hands.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
